{"action":"created","issue":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pydata/pydata-sphinx-theme/issues/2084","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pydata/pydata-sphinx-theme","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pydata/pydata-sphinx-theme/issues/2084/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pydata/pydata-sphinx-theme/issues/2084/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pydata/pydata-sphinx-theme/issues/2084/events","html_url":"https://github.com/pydata/pydata-sphinx-theme/issues/2084","id":2748858039,"node_id":"I_kwDOB8NEQs6j2D63","number":2084,"title":"SASS is deprecating `@import`","user":{"login":"stefanv","id":45071,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ1MDcx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45071?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv","html_url":"https://github.com/stefanv","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stefanv/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2024-12-18T22:20:39Z","updated_at":"2024-12-18T23:03:42Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"See https://sass-lang.com/documentation/breaking-changes/import/ and https://github.com/executablebooks/sphinx-design/issues/231

[Bootstrap issue](https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/issues/29853) (they're aiming for v6)

I think what we want in our `index.scss` is to do:

```
@use "sections/skip-link" as *;
```

For all modules we expose to users, but, interally, to use:

```
